The paper discusses an Explainable AI Planning (XAIP) agent that supports human decision making, which falls under the category of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The focus on visualization and transparency also suggests a potential fit for Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HCI). The use of planning components in a smart assistant for an instrumented meeting space could also relate to Robotics (cs.RO) and Systems and Control (cs.SY). Finally, the mention of model-based visualization suggests a possible connection to Machine Learning (cs.LG).
